      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine and transmission operate seamlessly, and all maintenance is fully up to date. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a car in showroom-quality condition with zero issues.",
