    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant damage, including large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul and currently struggles to stay running, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It will likely need to be towed from its current location.",
